                    <div class="col-MB-30">
                        <h2>BIO-WORLD TAKE NATURE SERIOUSLY!</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-9">
                    <h4>
                        We are inspired by nature. We are nature.
                    </h4>

                    <p>
                    In today’s fast-paced techno-driven life, we tend to forget how badly we are impacting Mother Nature on a day to day basis and its bad consequences in the future. It has become pivotal to bring some change now. We strongly believe that even one small contribution can also bring a huge difference to the environment and make it a much better place to live in. This is where Ekopak comes into the picture.

                    Ekopak is an eco-friendly tableware brand that provides complete single-use food packaging products for use in hospitals, corporate cafeterias, universities, restaurants, schools, homes, etc. All of our products are naturally compostable and suitable for hot, wet, and oily foods.

                    </p>
